      <div class="post post-723 type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-deans-perspectives tag-community tag-gratitude tag-veterinarians tag-veterinary-medicine" id="post-723">
       <div class="post-inner">
        <div class="post-header">
         <h2 class="post-title">
          <a href="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/2018/11/21/gratitude-and-hope-in-the-midst-of-tragedy/">
           Gratitude and Hope in the Midst of Tragedy
          </a>
         </h2>
         <div class="post-meta">
          <p class="post-author">
           <span>
            By
           </span>
           <a href="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/author/mlairmor/" rel="author" title="Posts by Michael Lairmore">
            Michael Lairmore
           </a>
          </p>
          <p class="post-date">
           <span>
            On
           </span>
           <a href="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/2018/11/21/gratitude-and-hope-in-the-midst-of-tragedy/">
            November 21, 2018
           </a>
          </p>
          <p class="post-categories">
           <span>
            In
           </span>
           <a href="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/category/deans-perspectives/" rel="category tag">
            Dean's Perspectives
           </a>
          </p>
         </div>
        </div>
        <!-- .post-header -->
        <div class="post-content">
         <p>
          <em>
           “Sometimes we should express our gratitude for the small and simple things like the scent of the rain, the taste of your favorite food, or the sound of a loved one’s voice. “
          </em>
          – Joseph B. Wirthlin
         </p>
         <div class="wp-caption alignright" id="attachment_718" style="width: 639px">
          <a href="http://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/11/IMG_E4097.jpg">
           <img alt="" class="size-large wp-image-718" height="472" sizes="(max-width: 629px) 100vw, 629px" src="http://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/11/IMG_E4097-1024x768.jpg" srcset="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/11/IMG_E4097-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/11/IMG_E4097-300x225.jpg 300w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/11/IMG_E4097-768x576.jpg 768w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/11/IMG_E4097-900x675.jpg 900w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/11/IMG_E4097-1280x960.jpg 1280w" width="629"/>
          </a>
          <p class="wp-caption-text">
           Galen Groff, a 3rd year DVM student, and Dr. Karen Park, a surgical resident, finish bandaging one of the cats rescued from the Camp Fire. He was later identified as Mayson and reunited with his owner.
          </p>
         </div>
         <p>
          As we look skyward through the gray smoke that hovers over us, waiting for the winter rains, it is a good time to reflect on the blessings around us each day.
         </p>
         <p>
          A holiday to express gratitude following the deadly California fires over the past several weeks is both timely and healing. From tragedy comes hope as we observe all those who came to help the animals and people affected by the fire.
         </p>
         <p>
          <a class="more-link" href="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/2018/11/21/gratitude-and-hope-in-the-midst-of-tragedy/">
           Read More
          </a>
         </p>
         <div class="rtsocial-container rtsocial-container-align-center rtsocial-icon">
          <div class="rtsocial-twitter-icon">
           <div class="rtsocial-twitter-icon-button">
            <a class="rtsocial-twitter-icon-link" href="https://twitter.com/share?text=Gratitude%20and%20Hope%20in%20the%20Midst%20of%20Tragedy&amp;via=LairmoreDVMDean&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu%2F2018%2F11%2F21%2Fgratitude-and-hope-in-the-midst-of-tragedy%2F" target="_blank" title="Tweet: Gratitude and Hope in the Midst of Tragedy">
            </a>
           </div>
          </div>
          <div class="rtsocial-fb-icon fb-light">
           <div class="rtsocial-fb-icon-button">
            <a class="rtsocial-fb-icon-link" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu%2F2018%2F11%2F21%2Fgratitude-and-hope-in-the-midst-of-tragedy%2F" target="_blank" title="Share: Gratitude and Hope in the Midst of Tragedy">
            </a>
           </div>
          </div>
          <div class="rtsocial-linkedin-icon">
           <div class="rtsocial-linkedin-icon-button">
            <a class="rtsocial-linkedin-icon-link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu%2F2018%2F11%2F21%2Fgratitude-and-hope-in-the-midst-of-tragedy%2F&amp;title=Gratitude+and+Hope+in+the+Midst+of+Tragedy" target="_blank" title="Share: Gratitude and Hope in the Midst of Tragedy">
            </a>
           </div>
          </div>
          <a class="perma-link" href="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/2018/11/21/gratitude-and-hope-in-the-midst-of-tragedy/" rel="nofollow" title="Gratitude and Hope in the Midst of Tragedy">
          </a>
