      <div class="post post-694 type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-deans-perspectives tag-alumni tag-leadership tag-passion tag-students tag-veterinary-medicine" id="post-694">
       <div class="post-inner">
        <div class="post-header">
         <h2 class="post-title">
          <a href="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/2018/10/17/honoring-our-alumni-foundation-to-our-success/">
           Honoring Our Alumni—Foundation to Our Success
          </a>
         </h2>
         <div class="post-meta">
          <p class="post-author">
           <span>
            By
           </span>
           <a href="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/author/mlairmor/" rel="author" title="Posts by Michael Lairmore">
            Michael Lairmore
           </a>
          </p>
          <p class="post-date">
           <span>
            On
           </span>
           <a href="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/2018/10/17/honoring-our-alumni-foundation-to-our-success/">
            October 17, 2018
           </a>
          </p>
          <p class="post-categories">
           <span>
            In
           </span>
           <a href="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/category/deans-perspectives/" rel="category tag">
            Dean's Perspectives
           </a>
          </p>
         </div>
        </div>
        <!-- .post-header -->
        <div class="post-content">
         <p>
          “
          <em>
           The biggest adventure you can take is to live the life of your dreams
          </em>
          .” –Oprah Winfrey
         </p>
         <p>
          <a href="http://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/45158860342_2d6e6311c6_k.jpg">
           <img alt="" class="alignright wp-image-700 size-large" height="420" sizes="(max-width: 629px) 100vw, 629px" src="http://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/45158860342_2d6e6311c6_k-1024x683.jpg" srcset="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/45158860342_2d6e6311c6_k-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/45158860342_2d6e6311c6_k-300x200.jpg 300w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/45158860342_2d6e6311c6_k-768x512.jpg 768w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/45158860342_2d6e6311c6_k-900x600.jpg 900w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/45158860342_2d6e6311c6_k-1280x853.jpg 1280w" width="629"/>
          </a>
          We recently hosted the combined Fall Festival and Alumni Reunion allowing us to welcome back our alumni to celebrate their memories of their time with us, their life accomplishments since graduation, and their contributions to the legacy of our school. The gathering featured major milestones for our alumni highlighted by events focused on the 50th and 60th reunions of the Classes of 1968 and 1958, respectively. During our traditional Rose Ceremony, we took time to focus on the Class of 1968 celebrating their 50th anniversary, in a poignant and heartwarming affair in which classmates shared stories, both humorous and touching, about themselves and those that have been lost over the years.
         </p>
         <p>
          <a href="http://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/IMG_E3377.jpg">
           <img alt="" class="alignleft wp-image-695 size-large" height="472" sizes="(max-width: 629px) 100vw, 629px" src="http://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/IMG_E3377-1024x768.jpg" srcset="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/IMG_E3377-1024x768.jpg 1024w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/IMG_E3377-300x225.jpg 300w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/IMG_E3377-768x576.jpg 768w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/IMG_E3377-900x675.jpg 900w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/IMG_E3377-1280x960.jpg 1280w" width="629"/>
          </a>
          I was particularly impressed by our Friday evening festivities, kicked off with special appearances by Gunrock (the UC Davis mascot) and an energetic performance by the UC Davis marching “Band-uh,” while alumni and current students enjoyed a BBQ dinner. After entertainment by the Uncovered band (comprised of several of our talented staff), current students took part in a talent show.
          <a href="http://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/45158609442_37e91e9444_k.jpg">
           <img alt="" class="alignright size-large wp-image-690" height="420" sizes="(max-width: 629px) 100vw, 629px" src="http://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/45158609442_37e91e9444_k-1024x683.jpg" srcset="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/45158609442_37e91e9444_k-1024x683.jpg 1024w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/45158609442_37e91e9444_k-300x200.jpg 300w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/45158609442_37e91e9444_k-768x512.jpg 768w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/45158609442_37e91e9444_k-900x600.jpg 900w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/45158609442_37e91e9444_k-1280x853.jpg 1280w" width="629"/>
          </a>
          Their singing, dancing, instrumental playing, and spirit overwhelmed many of our alumni who were impressed by our students’ energy, maturity, and talent.
         </p>
         <p>
          <a class="more-link" href="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/2018/10/17/honoring-our-alumni-foundation-to-our-success/">
           Read More
          </a>
         </p>
         <div class="rtsocial-container rtsocial-container-align-center rtsocial-icon">
          <div class="rtsocial-twitter-icon">
