      <div class="post post-681 type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-deans-perspectives tag-awards tag-excellence tag-faculty tag-research tag-teaching" id="post-681">
       <div class="post-inner">
        <div class="post-header">
         <h2 class="post-title">
          <a href="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/2018/10/02/our-commitment-to-excellence-reflected-in-faculty/">
           Our Commitment to Excellence Reflected in Faculty
          </a>
         </h2>
         <div class="post-meta">
          <p class="post-author">
           <span>
            By
           </span>
           <a href="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/author/mlairmor/" rel="author" title="Posts by Michael Lairmore">
            Michael Lairmore
           </a>
          </p>
          <p class="post-date">
           <span>
            On
           </span>
           <a href="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/2018/10/02/our-commitment-to-excellence-reflected-in-faculty/">
            October 2, 2018
           </a>
          </p>
          <p class="post-categories">
           <span>
            In
           </span>
           <a href="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/category/deans-perspectives/" rel="category tag">
            Dean's Perspectives
           </a>
          </p>
         </div>
        </div>
        <!-- .post-header -->
        <div class="post-content">
         <p>
          <em>
           “Productivity is never an accident. It is always the result of a commitment to excellence, intelligent planning, and focused effort.”
          </em>
          — Paul J. Meyer
         </p>
         <div class="wp-caption alignright" id="attachment_675" style="width: 410px">
          <a href="http://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/20180920FallRecpt033.jpg">
           <img alt="" class="wp-image-675 size-full" height="267" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" src="http://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/20180920FallRecpt033.jpg" srcset="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/20180920FallRecpt033.jpg 400w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/20180920FallRecpt033-300x200.jpg 300w" width="400"/>
          </a>
          <p class="wp-caption-text">
           Dean Michael Lairmore presents Dr. Ashley Hill an award for her work with the Masters of Preventative Medicine Program.
          </p>
         </div>
         <p>
          A major event that highlights the beginning of our academic year is our annual
          <a href="https://www.vetmed.ucdavis.edu/news/2018-fall-faculty-reception">
           Fall Faculty Reception
          </a>
          where we honor faculty members with awards for excellence in teaching and research. Our faculty include some of the most talented individuals in their discipline. They are accomplished educators and researchers who strive on a daily basis to bring their talents, work ethic, and innovations to accomplish our academic mission in teaching, research, and service to our communities. Our faculty are nationally and internationally recognized as leaders in their professional fields, therefore it is appropriate for us to recognize some of our best and brightest during our annual reception.
         </p>
         <div class="wp-caption alignleft" id="attachment_676" style="width: 410px">
          <a href="http://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/20180920FallRecpt036.jpg">
           <img alt="" class="wp-image-676 size-full" height="267" sizes="(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px" src="http://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/20180920FallRecpt036.jpg" srcset="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/20180920FallRecpt036.jpg 400w, https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/wp-content/uploads/sites/205/2018/10/20180920FallRecpt036-300x200.jpg 300w" width="400"/>
          </a>
          <p class="wp-caption-text">
           Dr. Joie Watson presents Dr. Stephan McSorley the 2018 Zoetis Distinguished Veterinary Teaching Award.
          </p>
         </div>
         <p>
          Dr. Stephen McSorley was honored with the Zoetis Distinguished Veterinary Teacher Award for his excellence in teaching immunology and microbiology and for outstanding block teaching leadership. His students consistently comment on his efforts to make a complicated topic more manageable, using a “road map” to organize lecture material that includes superhero references.
         </p>
         <p>
          <a class="more-link" href="https://lairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu/2018/10/02/our-commitment-to-excellence-reflected-in-faculty/">
           Read More
          </a>
         </p>
         <div class="rtsocial-container rtsocial-container-align-center rtsocial-icon">
          <div class="rtsocial-twitter-icon">
           <div class="rtsocial-twitter-icon-button">
            <a class="rtsocial-twitter-icon-link" href="https://twitter.com/share?text=Our%20Commitment%20to%20Excellence%20Reflected%20in%20Faculty&amp;via=LairmoreDVMDean&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2Four-commitment-to-excellence-reflected-in-faculty%2F" target="_blank" title="Tweet: Our Commitment to Excellence Reflected in Faculty">
            </a>
           </div>
          </div>
          <div class="rtsocial-fb-icon fb-light">
           <div class="rtsocial-fb-icon-button">
            <a class="rtsocial-fb-icon-link" href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Flairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2Four-commitment-to-excellence-reflected-in-faculty%2F" target="_blank" title="Share: Our Commitment to Excellence Reflected in Faculty">
            </a>
           </div>
          </div>
          <div class="rtsocial-linkedin-icon">
           <div class="rtsocial-linkedin-icon-button">
            <a class="rtsocial-linkedin-icon-link" href="https://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Flairvet.faculty.ucdavis.edu%2F2018%2F10%2F02%2Four-commitment-to-excellence-reflected-in-faculty%2F&amp;title=Our+Commitment+to+Excellence+Reflected+in+Faculty" target="_blank" title="Share: Our Commitment to Excellence Reflected in Faculty">
            </a>
           </div>
